             deposed that he was on board a Yatch, and seeing a Smoak went on Shoar about 2 a Clock in the Morning, that he saw a Man come out of the Reed-Loft, whom he deliver'd to Mr. Hawkins. 
               <persName id="t17200712-23-person159">
                  Matthew 
                  Hawkins 
               <interp inst="t17200712-23-person159" type="surname" value="Hawkins"></interp>
